quickly setting up development environment on ubuntu 11.04:
    install mysql server
    install apache2
    install php packages (for example by runnign: sudo ./install_php_packages.sh)

    execute following commands:
        sudo chmod a+wx /var/www
        cd /var/www 
        git clone git@github.com:betonek/betonek.git
        
    edit /etc/apache2/sites-available/default and change DocumentRoot to: /var/www/betonek/htdocs
    
        
   
